{"article_id":"vxg09ObPSzM2xP6U","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump and French President Emmanuel Macron appeared united on Saturday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"after contentious comments by both leaders","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that threatened to derail the celebration in France","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"marking 100 years since the end of World War I .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Trump attacked his French host upon arrival in France late Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"lashing out at Macron ' s \" very insulting \" suggestion","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that Europe needs to protect against \" China , Russia and even the United States of America . \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"\" President Macron of France has just suggested","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that Europe build its own military","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"in order to protect itself from the U.S. , China and Russia .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Very insulting ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"but perhaps Europe should first pay its fair share of NATO ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"which the U.S. subsidizes greatly ! \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"But the tension was all gone by Saturday","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"when the pair met at the Elysee Palace","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and appeared in agreement ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"with Macron calling Trump his \" good friend . \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"TRUMP RIPS MACRON","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"AFTER LANDING IN FRANCE OVER ' INSULTING ' CALL FOR EUROPEAN ARMY","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"Trump said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Macron \" understands","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that the United States can only do so much \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"and noted","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that the U.S. wants to help .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"\" You know what my attitude 's been ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and we want a strong Europe .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"It 's very important to us to have a strong Europe .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"And whichever way","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"we can do it the best and most efficient would be something","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"we both want , \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" We 're getting along from the standpoint of fairness ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and I want to be fair .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"We want to help Europe ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"but it has to be fair .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Right now the burden-sharing has been largely on the United States","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"as the President will say","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and he understands that .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"He understands","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the United States can only do so much . \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" You know what my attitude 's been ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and we want a strong Europe .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"It 's very important to us to have a strong Europe . '' - President Trump Macron agreed .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"\" I do share President Trump ' s views","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that we need a much better burden-sharing with NATO","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and that ' s why I do believe","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that my proposal for a European defense \" is \" utterly consistent with that . \"","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"MACRON POPULARITY PLUMMETS AT HOME","depth":3},{"id":49,"text":"AS HE PUSHES GLOBALISM ON WORLD STAGE","depth":3},{"id":50,"text":"Earlier this week , the French president made the comments about a European army in reference to Trump ' s decision","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"to withdraw from the 1987 Intermediate-Range Nuclear Forces Treaty with Russia .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"\" We will not protect the Europeans","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"unless we decide to have a true European army , \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Macron said ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"according to The Wall Street Journal .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"He went on to group the U.S. with the countries","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"from which France needed protecting .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"\" We have to protect ourselves with respect to China , Russia and even the United States of America , \"","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"he said on French radio .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Despite a friendly meeting in Washington in April ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"filled with back-slapping and warm greetings ,","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Macron has taken a number of swipes at Trump 's nationalism in recent months .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"In September , he spoke in front of the United Nations General Assembly","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"and criticized a unilateralist approach","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that entails `` a certain lawlessness","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"where everyone pursues their own interests . ''","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"\" I will never stop upholding the principle of sovereignty","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"even in the face of a certain nationalism ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"which we ' re seeing today ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"brandishing sovereignty as a way","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"of attacking others , ''","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"just hours after Trump addressed the General Assembly .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"Trump is joining a number of other world leaders on Sunday for a ceremony in the shadow of the Arc de Triomphe","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"to mark the WWI centennial .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":123,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":93,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":79,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":0,"right":78,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":1,"right":77,"relat